These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Flower   | orchid  | daffodil |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, june
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Birthday    | april      | june         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, collecting
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Hobby   | collecting | singing   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
